{
 "nodes": [
  {
   "id": "title",
   "type": "text",
   "x": 0,
   "y": -130,
   "width": 2430,
   "height": 80,
   "text": "# \ud83e\udd9b Hippo \u2014 Dev Progress\nRoadmap (top) \u00b7 Kanban (below) \u2014 snapshot: July 18, 2026. Full detail: [[00 Build Plan Overview]] \u00b7 [[Open Decisions]] \u00b7 [[Home]]"
  },
  {
   "id": "g0",
   "type": "group",
   "x": 0,
   "y": 0,
   "width": 380,
   "height": 360,
   "label": "Phase 0 \u2014 Foundations",
   "color": "4"
  },
  {
   "id": "c0",
   "type": "text",
   "x": 15,
   "y": 45,
   "width": 350,
   "height": 300,
   "text": "**Weeks 1\u20132 \u00b7 \u2705 done**\n\n- Card protocol v1 (Zod, additive-only + fallback)\n- Eval harness v1 (300 queries, launch gates)\n- CI: build/test/size-gate/lint per PR"
  },
  {
   "id": "g1",
   "type": "group",
   "x": 410,
   "y": 0,
   "width": 380,
   "height": 360,
   "label": "Phase 1 \u2014 Thin Client SDK",
   "color": "4"
  },
  {
   "id": "c1",
   "type": "text",
   "x": 425,
   "y": 45,
   "width": 350,
   "height": 300,
   "text": "**Weeks 2\u20136 \u00b7 \u2705 done (Jul 16)**\n\n- Core renderer, onboarding, share/feedback, mock-gateway demo\n- Posture matrix + tokenized themes (#12) \u00b7 i18n + RTL (#15)\n- **Fold release** (`629251b`): contextual chips, composer v2 + drafts, scroll anchoring, offline outbox, a11y, settings (language + clear memory), brief copy \u2014 108 tests\n- Remaining: Arabic copy (layout works, strings pending)"
  },
  {
   "id": "g2",
   "type": "group",
   "x": 820,
   "y": 0,
   "width": 380,
   "height": 360,
   "label": "Phase 2 \u2014 Intelligence Backend",
   "color": "3"
  },
  {
   "id": "c2",
   "type": "text",
   "x": 835,
   "y": 45,
   "width": 350,
   "height": 300,
   "text": "**Weeks 4\u201310 \u00b7 \ud83d\udea7 nearly done**\n\n- Intelligence service merged (#8): intent + research, answer cache, guardrail, SSE streaming\n- Gateway core merged (#7) + streaming briefs (#9)\n- Memory v1 merged (#10) \u00b7 Redis stores + OTel (#13)\n- Full loop verified live on qwen3:4b + market data\n- Open: the bake-off run vs 70B baseline (needs GPU)"
  },
  {
   "id": "g3",
   "type": "group",
   "x": 1230,
   "y": 0,
   "width": 380,
   "height": 360,
   "label": "Phase 3 \u2014 Execution Seam",
   "color": "3"
  },
  {
   "id": "c3",
   "type": "text",
   "x": 1245,
   "y": 45,
   "width": 350,
   "height": 300,
   "text": "**Weeks 8\u201312 \u00b7 \ud83d\udea7 in progress**\n\n- Seam service + sim venue extracted from orchestrator\n- **Hand-built KoinBX adapter** (HMAC private trade API) + poll reconciler + audit log\n- Approach A locked (Open Decision #1)\n- Open: pilot-sandbox lifecycle round-trip \u00b7 confirm-surface mode (Decision #6)"
  },
  {
   "id": "g4",
   "type": "group",
   "x": 1640,
   "y": 0,
   "width": 380,
   "height": 360,
   "label": "Phase 4 \u2014 Agentic Installer",
   "color": "3"
  },
  {
   "id": "c4",
   "type": "text",
   "x": 1655,
   "y": 45,
   "width": 350,
   "height": 300,
   "text": "**Weeks 10\u201314 \u00b7 \ud83d\udea7 in progress**\n\n- `hippo scan v0` (discovery \u2192 integration report)\n- CTI conformance suite + `hippo conform`\n- Stage 3: deterministic adapter.config.yaml generator\n- Stage 4: mapping.ts + rejections.yaml codegen\n- Open: embed injection \u00b7 second-venue dogfood"
  },
  {
   "id": "g5",
   "type": "group",
   "x": 2050,
   "y": 0,
   "width": 380,
   "height": 360,
   "label": "Phase 5 \u2014 Pilot Launch",
   "color": "6"
  },
  {
   "id": "c5",
   "type": "text",
   "x": 2065,
   "y": 45,
   "width": 350,
   "height": 300,
   "text": "**Weeks 12\u201316 \u00b7 \u2b1c not started**\n\n- Onboarding hero live, ambient pulse, share cards (client parts shipped in Phase 1)\n- Pilot instrumentation: cache hit rate, queries/MAU, cost/MAU, lift telemetry\n- Degraded-mode banner demonstrable for procurement"
  },
  {
   "id": "kb-backlog",
   "type": "group",
   "x": 0,
   "y": 420,
   "width": 460,
   "height": 500,
   "label": "\ud83d\udccb Backlog",
   "color": "6"
  },
  {
   "id": "bl1",
   "type": "text",
   "x": 15,
   "y": 480,
   "width": 430,
   "height": 85,
   "text": "Bake-off run vs 70B baseline \u2014 Phase 2 exit gate (needs GPU access)"
  },
  {
   "id": "bl3",
   "type": "text",
   "x": 15,
   "y": 580,
   "width": 430,
   "height": 85,
   "text": "Pilot-sandbox lifecycle round-trip \u2014 Phase 3 exit gate, all cards from real venue events"
  },
  {
   "id": "bl5",
   "type": "text",
   "x": 15,
   "y": 680,
   "width": 430,
   "height": 85,
   "text": "Second-venue CLI dogfood \u2014 regenerate KoinBX adapter, diff vs hand-built"
  },
  {
   "id": "bl6",
   "type": "text",
   "x": 15,
   "y": 780,
   "width": 430,
   "height": 85,
   "text": "Pilot instrumentation \u2014 cache hit rate, queries/MAU, cost/MAU, lift telemetry"
  },
  {
   "id": "kb-progress",
   "type": "group",
   "x": 500,
   "y": 420,
   "width": 460,
   "height": 700,
   "label": "\ud83d\udea7 In Progress",
   "color": "3"
  },
  {
   "id": "ip1",
   "type": "text",
   "x": 515,
   "y": 480,
   "width": 430,
   "height": 85,
   "text": "Admin panel (`feat/admin-panel`) \u2014 controller, live-session kill switch, operator mgmt, login lockout, durable MAU, quota alerts"
  },
  {
   "id": "ip2",
   "type": "text",
   "x": 515,
   "y": 580,
   "width": 430,
   "height": 85,
   "text": "Point the site demo default at the real gateway (?gw=real exists; flip the default post-pilot-wiring)"
  },
  {
   "id": "kb-blocked",
   "type": "group",
   "x": 1000,
   "y": 420,
   "width": 460,
   "height": 400,
   "label": "\u26d4 Blocked / Open Decisions",
   "color": "1"
  },
  {
   "id": "bk1",
