   "x": 1015,
   "y": 480,
   "width": 430,
   "height": 85,
   "text": "Confirm-surface mode \u2014 API (pilot default) vs deep link vs JS callback vs hosted modal \u2014 Decision #6, with pilot partner eng"
  },
  {
   "id": "bk2",
   "type": "text",
   "x": 1015,
   "y": 580,
   "width": 430,
   "height": 85,
   "text": "Layer-2 consent format per jurisdiction \u2014 counsel, before first Gulf contract (Decision #2)"
  },
  {
   "id": "bk3",
   "type": "text",
   "x": 1015,
   "y": 680,
   "width": 430,
   "height": 85,
   "text": "CLI agent model \u2014 frontier vs open-source codegen (Decision #3) \u2014 blocks init stages 5\u20136 polish"
